newKeys[note][noteKey][noteSelection] = !newKeys[note][noteKey][noteSelection]; }; // Inherit from global const previews const [preview, setPrevSelection] = useState(previews[0]); const togglePreview = (prev) => { let prevResult = previews.filter((_prev) => _prev.previewStatus !== prev.previewStatus);
